  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "qDs/YZvtnu6tTHEA12XEhTlaIl4=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# resource-instance model tracks provisioned resource lifecycle\n\n`powerhouse/resource-instance` represents a provisioned resource for a customer. It has a detailed lifecycle with provisioning, suspension, and termination states.\n\n## State Shape\n\n```graphql\ntype ResourceInstanceState {\n    resourceTemplateId: PHID       # \u2192 ResourceTemplate\n    customerId: PHID               # \u2192 customer identity (external)\n    name: String\n    profile: ResourceProfile       # { id: PHID!, documentType: String! }\n    status: InstanceStatus!        # DRAFT | PROVISIONING | ACTIVE | SUSPENDED | TERMINATED\n    configuration: [InstanceFacet!]!\n    # ... lifecycle timestamps, suspension details\n}\n```\n\n## Modules (2)\n\n| Module | Operations | Purpose |\n|--------|-----------|---------|\n| instance-management | 14 | Initialize, update info, status transitions, provisioning, suspension (non-payment/maintenance), termination |\n| configuration-management | 4 | Set/remove/update instance facets, apply configuration changes |\n\n## Key References\n\n- `resourceTemplateId: PHID` \u2192 ResourceTemplate\n- `customerId: PHID` \u2192 customer identity (external)\n- `profile.id: PHID` \u2192 external profile document\n- SubscriptionInstance.`resource.id` \u2192 references this model\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[schema design]]\n- [[object relations]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z"
    }
  },
